# Project language

- Write **English** only in this repo: READMEs, `AGENTS.md`, `ai-rules/`, skills, specs, plans, code comments, tests, and CLI/help copy.
- Do not introduce non-English prose for new content unless quoting an external source.
- The language rule is also indexed in root **`AGENTS.md`**.
